getDefaultDevTime

public void getDefaultDevTime()
                       throws java.lang.Exception
Test that GET {host}/devtime/{user}/default/{starttime} works properly. First, it creates a test user and sends some sample DevEvent data to the SensorBase. Then, it invokes the GET request and checks to see that it obtains the right answer. Finally, it deletes the data and the user.

Throws:
java.lang.Exception - If problems occur.
